Pablo Andrés Rivero[寫到](http://www.pabloarivero.com/2011/06/fotografiando-el-
gran-poder.html "http://www.pabloarivero.com/2011/06/fotografiando-el-gran-
poder.html")[西文]拉巴斯的[Gran
Poder](http://www.boliviahostels.com/travelguide/festivals.html#poder
"http://www.boliviahostels.com/travelguide/festivals.html#poder")慶典。Pablo記述了慶典遊行的音樂、舞蹈與色彩繽紛的服裝，並提供他在[Flickr](http://www.flickr.com/photos/parivero/sets/72157626874044155/
"http://www.flickr.com/photos/parivero/sets/72157626874044155/")上的活動照片連結，這些照片依據創用CC授權。

